SUMMARY:Abolition Pub-Ed: Elene Lam and Butterfly - by Disability Justice
  Network of Ontario
LOCATION:Virtual
DESCRIPTION:More info:
  https://djno-ca.zoom.us/meeting/register/lZPcLeXrRi-5LQW-aYU0rA#/registra
 tion\n\nHosted by Disability Justice Network of Ontario
  (https://www.djno.ca/)\n\nElene Lam and Butterfly (Asian and Migrant Sex
  Workers Support Network) will share about the stigma\, issues\, and risks
  faced by migrant sex workers (e.g. targeting by police\, conflation of
  sex work with human trafficking) and how to transition from "we can't
  call the police" to "we don't have to call the police” to keep each
  other safe.
END:VEVENT
